ngOnChanges() - whenever you want to detect changes from a variable decorated by @Input.it track the change detection with non premitive data types
ngOnInit()
ngDoCheck() - whenever you want to detect changes from a variable decorated by @Input.it track the change detection with premitive data types
ngAfterContentInit() - @ContentChild()
ngAfterContentChecked()
ngAfterViewInit() - when you want to call a lifecycle hook after all child components have been initialized and checked. @viewChild, @viewChildren
ngAfterViewChecked()
ngOnDestroy()
